<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٤٨٤٦ - <span class="c2">«كان لا يدخر شيئا لغد»</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
